Utilities for touch devices
===========================

# calibrate-touch
-----------------

Useful for multiple screens when only one of them has touch digitizer on it. This is usually the case with touch-enabled laptops when you attach additional monitors.
It will update the coordination system based on your current setup.

# rotate-screen

Script for rotating devices like the Lenovo Yoga. It will rotate your screen 180 degree and will update the touch calibration.
